# Changelog

All notable changes to SproutSmart will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Planned Features
- Voice command support for hands-free operation
- Multi-language interface (Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali)
- Community forum for urban farmers
- AR visualization for farming setups
- Smart notifications based on weather patterns
- Integration with IoT sensors

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-02-07

### ðŸŽ‰ Initial Release

#### Added
- **Waste Classification System**
  - CNN-based image classification using MobileNetV2
  - Support for plastic bottles, containers, and various household waste
  - Size and structure estimation from uploaded images
  - Trained model with 95%+ accuracy

- **Farming Structure Generation**
  - cGAN-powered design generation for upcycled farming setups
  - Support for three farming methods:
    - Soil-based farming
    - Hydroponics
    - Aeroponics
  - Step-by-step construction instructions

- **Plant Recommendation Engine**
  - Hoeffding tree-based decision system
  - Considers multiple factors:
    - Waste material size and type
    - Local weather conditions
    - Climate zone
    - Regional suitability
  - Suggests herbs, vegetables, and decorative plants

- **Weather Integration**
  - OpenWeatherMap API integration
  - Real-time weather data for farming decisions
  - Region-specific climate analysis
  - Weather-adaptive plant care suggestions

- **Organic Manure Guide**
  - Liquid manure preparation from kitchen scraps
  - Simple, no-effort methods
  - Cost savings calculator
  - Storage and usage instructions

- **Natural Pest Control**
  - Organic pesticide preparation guide
  - Kitchen scrap-based solutions
  - Disease prevention tips
  - Chemical-free farming support

- **Mobile Application**
  - Android app interface
  - Camera integration for waste image upload
  - Stage-wise cultivation guidance
  - User-friendly, prompt-free design

- **Core Features**
  - Image processing pipeline
  - Cloud-based model training (Google Colab)
  - Efficient mobile performance
  - Offline capability for core features

#### Technical Specifications
- Python 3.9+ support
- TensorFlow 2.15.0
- PyTorch 2.1.0
- MobileNetV2 for classification
- Flask-based API backend
- Android Studio integration

#### Documentation
- Comprehensive README
- Installation guide
- API documentation
- User manual
- Video demonstrations

---

## [0.9.0-beta] - 2024-12-15

### Beta Release for Testing

#### Added
- Beta version of waste classification
- Initial plant recommendation logic
- Basic weather API integration
- Prototype mobile interface

#### Changed
- Improved model accuracy from 85% to 92%
- Enhanced UI/UX based on user feedback
- Optimized image processing speed

#### Fixed
- Image upload crash on certain Android devices
- Weather API timeout issues
- Memory leaks in classification module

---

## [0.5.0-alpha] - 2024-10-01

### Alpha Release for Internal Testing

#### Added
- Proof of concept for waste classification
- Basic CNN model implementation
- Simple plant database
- Initial Android app prototype

#### Known Issues
- Limited waste material types (5 categories only)
- No weather integration
- Manual prompt required for plant selection
- Performance issues on older devices

---

